小舅婆在战“疫”前线战斗，有有做了战地后方的“小记者”。
My brother-in-law in the "epidemic" front-line combat, there are back in the field to do "small reporters."
画画内容的变化也悄然诉说着疫情的变化。
Changes in the content of the painting are also quietly telling the story of the epidemic.
编者按当很多小朋友把寒假过得快腻味的时候，有个叫有有的小朋友，却找到了一件有趣的持之以恒的事情——画抗疫漫画。
Editor's Note: When many children pass the winter vacation quickly boring, there is a child called there is, but found an interesting and persistent thing - draw anti-epidemic caricatures.
有有，大名蔡亦澄，是一个喜欢画画的6岁小女孩。
Yes, Dai Yicheng is a 6-year-old girl who likes to paint.
孩子的小舅婆（也就是孩子妈妈的舅妈）是仁济医院呼吸科的医生查琼芳，她在除夕夜随第一批援鄂医疗队出征武汉。
The child's younger brother-in-law, the mother's aunt, was a doctor at Yan Chai Hospital's respiratory department, Cha Qiongfang, who accompanied the first medical team to Hubei on New Year's Eve.
因为舅婆的出征，孩子对新冠肺炎疫情的发展格外关注，也格外关心在前线奋战的小舅婆。
Because my aunt's war, the child is especially concerned about the development of the new crown pneumonia, but also pays special attention to the younger brother-in-law fighting in the front.
这次画画的起点就是从画小舅婆开始，之后她开始通过每天的新闻报道寻找画画的素材。
The starting point of the painting was to start with my mother-in-law, and then she began to look for material for her daily news stories.
每天中午和晚上的新闻是雷打不动必须要看的，上海台的新闻看完，还要看中央台的，每每看到新闻中她感兴趣的内容，就要求妈妈拍下来。
Every day noon and evening news is not thunderous must see, Shanghai Radio news read, but also to see the central station, often see the news she is interested in, asked her mother to film.
现在她依旧每天都兴致勃勃地期待着“画画时间”，她像一个小记者一样，用画画这个特殊的方式“报道”着疫情的发展。
She is still looking forward to "painting time" every day. Like a small journalist, she "reports" on the development of the epidemic in a special way.
家里人都笑称：小舅婆在战“疫”前线战斗，有有做了战地后方的“小记者”。
The family laughed and said: uncle in-law in the "epidemic" front-line battle, there have been a field back "small reporters."
画画内容的变化也悄然诉说着疫情的变化：从最初的医院建设到各种物资支援，从隔离点的关怀到患者陆续出院，相信很快能看到医疗队员们凯旋、武汉春暖花开的美丽画面。
The changes in the content of the painting also speak of the change in the epidemic: from the initial construction of the hospital to various material support, from the care of isolation points to the gradual discharge of patients, I believe that the medical team will soon be able to see the triumph of the medical team, Wuhan beautiful picture of spring flowers.
这个史上最漫长的寒假想必会给她留下深刻的印象，而这一幅幅图画不仅将成为她一生的珍贵回忆，也给我们留下一段可爱又感人的记录。
She is sure to be impressed by the longest winter vacation in history, a picture that will not only be a treasured memory of her life, but also leave us a lovely and moving record.
